@startuml
title [RF006] - Alterar Senha

actor User as "Usuário/ONG"
participant UI as "Interface UI"
participant Backend as "Back End"
database DB as "Banco de Dados"

User ->> UI: Informa senha atual e nova
UI ->> Backend: PUT /api/usuarios/senha
Backend ->> DB: SELECT senha_atual
DB -->> Backend: Retorna senha
Backend ->> DB: UPDATE senha=...
DB -->> Backend: Sucesso
Backend -->> UI: Senha alterada
UI -->> User: Confirmação
@enduml
